<br>
Now, give me a fast 1h that proc's Envenombed Bolt or Aystole and now you're talking!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Depending on who you adventure with and how important DPS is to you, items that taunt well in your price range are the old Seb golden-oldies of the Journeymans Walking Stick (proc's Tash) and the Silken Whip of Ensnaring (proc's snare).  Both still generate good aggro and are cheap.  Kunzar Ku'juch proc's Engulfing Darkness (necro snare/dot) which is pretty good aggro, as well...though harder to stick than anything else listed, and it's damage/delay ratio hasn't stood the test of time very well. <p>Good travels,<br>
